# Walkthrough — GoLive Phase 2 Expansion 🚀

## Phase 2: Modernization & Discovery

We've successfully modernized the core navigation and added three major new sections to the platform.

### 1. Modern Collapsible Sidebar
- **New Feature**: Clicking the "Menu" icon now toggles between full width and a sleek "mini mode".
- **2026 Design**: Added active state glows, proper glassmorphism, and smooth transitions.
- **Mini Mode**: Shows only icons for navigation and avatars for live channels.

### 2. New Pages Implemented

#### [Trending Page](file:///C:/GoLive/app/trending/page.tsx)
- **Features**: Rank badges (#1, #2), horizontal "viral" card layout.
- **Algorithm**: Mock implementation sorting by `Views + Likes - TimeDecay`.

#### [Following Page](file:///C:/GoLive/app/subscriptions/page.tsx)
- **Features**: Filter chips (All, Today, Live Now) and a focused video grid.
- **Goal**: Clean space for users to catch up on their favorite content.

#### [Creator Dashboard](file:///C:/GoLive/app/dashboard/page.tsx)
- **Analytics**: Real-time overview of Views, Subscribers, and Revenue.
- **Content Management**: A data table to manage uploads (Edit/Delete).
- **Quick Upload**: Accessible button to drop new content.

